The input array `sentences` is not null.
The length of the input array `sentences` is greater than or equal to 1.
Each element in the input array `sentences` is not null.
Each element in the input array `sentences` is a valid sentence (a list of words separated by a single space).
Each element in the input array `sentences` does not have leading or trailing spaces.
All the words in each element of the input array `sentences` are separated by a single space.
